snippet.textDisplay:
I would be glad if YOU read it:
Enjoy
The reason why I love itzy is because they are different.
Everything about them is different.
They have energy and confidence enough to make us feel the same way.
They have *heathy bodies*. Gosh!
That is so important.
They are unique.
When you talk about ITZY, you talk about :
5 main singers
5 main dancers
5 main visuals
5 main everything
And that is what make us cheer for them the most.
I don't have a defined bias 😂
I cheer for all but LIA caught my attention.
There are K-POP groups that haven't released a album for a year (not mention ing name 😶), some releases a super mini album etc
But itzy just blessed us with 7 SONGS WHY ARE YOU MOANING ABOUT?
Of course that everybody has their own opinions about the songs.
But...
BLAMING MEMBERS FOR GETTING MORE SECONDS? THAT IS NOT COOL.
Itzy is different from other groups.
I feel like we as midzy, we also need to be different from other fandoms spread my word pls.
We need to change to. Hate on members?
No. That is for other groups and other fandoms.
Let's change that.
Let's be patient.
We all understood that in each cameback there is a member to focus on.
Three members got their chance. Two left to go. Only *two*.
If a member did get more chances that the others let's cheer for them not dragg them down and hate on her on only her.
The music, the album is already made. The dance is already made.
And if you hate it, hate it all.
If you love it, love it all with all your heart and make good criticism about what they could improve.
They will listen
Just
Don't pick one target.
Let's be different.
Let's speak good words.



(Gosh! I am inspired today 😂😁)
